Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在背後撞我車子的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開什麽玩笑 那不是你的錯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒想到前面在跑的家夥技術那麽差
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒預料會有人用這麽慢的速度入彎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒來得及踩Brake就撞上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麽！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 池谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要我道歉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按我們的規則進行一次比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們贏了的話 我就誠心誠意地向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的規則 是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麽大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們叫做膠布Death Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠布Death Match…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speed Stars不是有下坡第一人的86嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我轉告那個86小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下星期六晚十點 我在這等他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣了 Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥怎麽回事 是要向拓海挑戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他好像不認識拓海的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海 應戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠布Death Match還是什麽都好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那種家夥打敗 讓他跪下道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑了 太危險了 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不能扭盡轪盤的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是池谷前輩 拓海連FD和32都能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上點規則也不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方肯定在這種條件下作了很多練級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海 這麽亂來的比賽 絕對不要接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點點比賽的意思都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用理這樣的家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？膠布Death Match
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣太危險了 那麽拓海的意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是平常的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是冷靜還是不會被激怒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來沒有興趣比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想要拓海去跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個渾蛋打敗讓他下跪 這樣才夠痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方又是我們Levin和APEX的宿命車型Civil
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們年輕時也有設置規則或限制來做各種比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而膠布Death Match是最危險的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠布Death Match就眞的那麽危險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒沒怎麽感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹 你坐上車子試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 你的右手別放開轪盤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣用盡全力扭向任何一個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也扭不過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 轪盤不要動 你下車來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己看看車輪轉了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完…完全沒有轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經盡力扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話要如何轉彎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒辦法跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轪盤只是用來制造機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就只能靠滑動後輪來過彎了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的彎道都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Drift可是拓海的強項
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的想象中的那麽簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能完全Counter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.73,注釋,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,──────────────\N「Counter Steer」逆轉轪盤。\NDrift中進入打滑狀態時要往反\N方向打轪盤來保持行車路線。\N這裏就是說反打轪盤時也不能夠\N完全扭盡轪盤。\N────────{\fn黑体}{\i1}{\fs15}{\b1}{\fscx130}Initial D
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drift就會變得非常難以控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要稍微有一點Over Steer就一命嗚呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.23,重疊對白,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(368,430)}「轉向過度」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在入彎的時候出現Under Steer的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是相同命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這規則完全是讓FF有利而訂制的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是EG6吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FF的EG6的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用油門來抑制Over Steer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可以全速衝入彎道 用手刹來消除Under
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像86這樣的FR要想不出意外跑完全程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得在每個狹窄弧度又小的彎道以精確的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drift來控制轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不應戰是明智之舉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了 被拓海聽到這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他反而會想去出賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…店長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是健二前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池谷 關于上次那個腦袋壞掉的家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該就是妙義Night Kids的莊司慎吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Night Kids的莊司慎吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說目前是NO.2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對Down Hill非常有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以自稱是Night Kids下坡最快的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為了達到目的會不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其他隊員眼中不太受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是和隊長中裏毅關系非常不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 所以才想挑戰拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借此取得Night Kids的主導權
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥對這次的事 已經放出了奇怪的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠言？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說Speed Stars膽怯 在逃避慎吾的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又不敢接受膠布Death Match
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我們的顔面何存？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家夥還眞幹得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他無論如何也要把拓海拉出來應戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我嗎？不關我事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒打算要應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是 就算怎麽樣被挑戰也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒必要接受這種無理的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 和86比賽的事情怎麽樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隨時都OK 只是在等對方的回應而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正走著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把86的小鬼拉出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…看來會是一場有趣的比賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎吾 你最近在搞些奇怪的小動作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麽都是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不要把Night Kids的名聲抹黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽好笑的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名聲抹黑的是你這渾蛋才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被過時的86擊敗了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麽地方的什麽人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是擁有強勁馬力的32
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗家之犬還能亂吠 到是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但別總只擺著一副領隊的架子來說教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眞是大笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中裏 你的面子我會幫你拾回的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎吾 你遲早也會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台86的可怕之處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎…毅先生也墜落了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起Night Kids的領隊是你才對 慎吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 先把那台86送進解體場後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…我叫武內…我想找…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是佐代理嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…當然記得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名公園兜風？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 在上次的巴士站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點鍾在那等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那麽再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能從沒有女朋友一族裏脫出了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情暢快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:10:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠布Death Match…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了 沒什麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠布Death Match嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車的技術眞好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…如果是拓海的話…可以喲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的事情 我非常在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹在幹什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在洗車…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你躲在這裏偷懶呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不是…那個 稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還眞少見啊 樹居然會看書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…啊…這是個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽什麽…戀愛方程式？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生捕獵大法？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…所以…這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹會看這種書的話 那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次說的那個可愛的佐代理嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了 不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是順路經過所以買了 這本書我已經看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事 就算問前輩你也不明白的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還眞敢說！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說中了也沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還有這麽方便的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們那個年代全部都要自己策劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽怎麽…女生在第三次約會就會作出決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻要在一個浪漫的情況下進行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…我已經全部記得了 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麽回事 上次和你說的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能給我放假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麽回事吧 那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這臭小鬼好讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定時刻到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代理在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這呢 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是來加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來要上次說膠布Death Match的答複
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好地傳達給86的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全沒有興趣比賽 他是這麽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可怎麽行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來秋名的86是這麽窩囊廢的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是膠布Death Match就嚇得要逃了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他不願意 我也有辦法讓他出賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們車手稱呼轉彎是叫攻彎的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有點想考車牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考吧 我會教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 我會考慮一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名山…好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…女生對氣氛很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻要在浪漫的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是絕佳的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛好沈重啊…傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EG6
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用防護杆來撞我…是在嫌我慢叫我讓路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被咬住了 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽能在佐代理前面出醜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代理…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要飛車了…一會就好 稍微忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是車手間的勝負啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會罷手的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐…只要佐代理沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大件事了 樹出意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是秋名山道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經被送進市立醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個馬上去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微玩過火了 其實傷勢沒什麽大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一需要全面檢查 所以要住幾天醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代理呢？你們在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她只是擦傷而已 已經回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了不讓她受傷 拼命轉過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子呢？85怎麽樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利做了Spin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要換一兩件東西就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了 要保重身體喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了秋名湖以後 EG6就從背後出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EG6？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概沒錯 因為也是紅色的EG6
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入彎的時候突然從後面撞了我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個渾蛋 又來這一招
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠布Death Match也好 什麽都行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應戰就應戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要中他計啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠布Death Match太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸的 無論什麽樣的比賽
